#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:275
msgid "ChatTTS Usage"
msgstr "Uso do ChatTTS"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:277
#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:480
msgid "Basic usage, refer to :ref:`audio speech usage <audio_speech>`."
msgstr ""
"Uso básico, consulte a seção :ref:`Uso de áudio e fala <audio_speech>`."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:279
msgid ""
"Fixed tone color. We can use fixed tone color provided by "
"https://github.com/6drf21e/ChatTTS_Speaker, Download the "
"`evaluation_result.csv "
"<https://github.com/6drf21e/ChatTTS_Speaker/blob/main/evaluation_results.csv>`_"
" , take ``seed_2155`` as example, we get the ``emb_data`` of it."
msgstr ""
"Timbre fixo. Podemos usar o timbre fixo fornecido por "
"https://github.com/6drf21e/ChatTTS_Speaker, baixar o `evaluation_result.csv "
"<https://github.com/6drf21e/ChatTTS_Speaker/blob/main/evaluation_results.csv>`_,"
" e usar o timbre ``seed_2155`` como exemplo, empregando os dados da coluna "
"``emb_data``."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:292
msgid "Use the fixed tone color of ``seed_2155`` to generate speech."
msgstr "Use ``seed_2155`` para fixar o timbre e criar a voz."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:308
msgid "CosyVoice Usage"
msgstr "Uso do modelo CosyVoice"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:310
msgid ""
"CosyVoice has two versions: CosyVoice 1.0 and CosyVoice 2.0. CosyVoice 1.0 "
"has three different models:"
msgstr ""
"O CosyVoice possui duas versões: CosyVoice 1.0 e CosyVoice 2.0. O CosyVoice "
"1.0 tem 3 modelos diferentes:"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:312
msgid ""
"**CosyVoice-300M-SFT**: Choose this model if you just want to convert text "
"to audio. There are pretrained voices available: ['中文女', '中文男', '日语男', "
"'粤语女', '英文女', '英文男', '韩语女']"
msgstr ""
"**CosyVoice-300M-SFT**: Se você deseja apenas converter texto em fala, "
"escolha este modelo. Ele oferece alguns timbres pré-treinados: ['Voz "
"Feminina Chinesa', 'Voz Masculina Chinesa', 'Voz Masculina Japonesa', 'Voz "
"Feminina Cantonense', 'Voz Feminina Inglesa', 'Voz Masculina Inglesa', 'Voz "
"Feminina Coreana']"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:313
msgid ""
"**CosyVoice-300M**: Choose this model if you want to clone voice or convert "
"text to audio in different languages. The ``prompt_speech`` is always "
"required and should be a WAV file. For optimal performance, use a sample "
"rate of 16,000 Hz."
msgstr ""
"**CosyVoice-300M**: Se você deseja clonar voz ou converter texto em fala de "
"outro idioma, selecione este modelo. Para usá-lo, você deve fornecer um "
"arquivo de áudio ``prompt_speech`` no formato WAV, utilizando uma taxa de "
"amostragem de 16.000 Hz para obter melhor desempenho."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:314
msgid ""
"**CosyVoice-300M-Instruct**: Choose this model If you need precise control "
"over the tone and pitch."
msgstr ""
"**CosyVoice-300M-Instruct**: Se você deseja controlar com precisão o tom e o"
" timbre, escolha este modelo."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:316
msgid "Basic usage, launch model ``CosyVoice-300M-SFT``."
msgstr "Uso básico, carregue o modelo ``CosyVoice-300M-SFT``."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:365
msgid "Clone voice, launch model ``CosyVoice-300M``."
msgstr "Clonar voz, carregar o modelo ``CosyVoice-300M``."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:395
msgid "Cross lingual usage, launch model ``CosyVoice-300M``."
msgstr "Uso multilíngue, carregue o modelo ``CosyVoice-300M``."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:418
msgid "Instruction based, launch model ``CosyVoice-300M-Instruct``."
msgstr ""
"Síntese de voz baseada em instruções, carregue o modelo "
"``CosyVoice-300M-Instruct``."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:435
msgid ""
"CosyVoice 2.0 only has one model, it provides all the capabilities of the "
"three CosyVoice models. The usage is the same as CosyVoice."
msgstr ""
"CosyVoice 2.0 possui apenas um modelo, mas contém todas as capacidades dos "
"três modelos do CosyVoice. O método de uso é o mesmo do CosyVoice."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:437
msgid "CosyVoice 2.0 stream usage, launch model ``CosyVoice2-0.5B``."
msgstr ""
"Uso em streaming do CosyVoice 2.0, carregando o modelo ``CosyVoice2-0.5B``."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:474
msgid ""
"More instructions and examples, could be found at https://fun-audio-"
"llm.github.io/ ."
msgstr ""
"Mais instruções e exemplos podem ser encontrados em https://fun-audio-"
"llm.github.io/."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:478
msgid "FishSpeech Usage"
msgstr "Modelo FishSpeech"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:482
msgid ""
"Clone voice, launch model ``FishSpeech-1.5``. Please use `prompt_speech` "
"instead of `reference_audio` and `prompt_text` instead of `reference_text` "
"to clone voice from the reference audio for the FishSpeech model. This "
"arguments is aligned to voice cloning of CosyVoice."
msgstr ""
"Clone a voz, iniciando o modelo ``FishSpeech-1.5``. Use `prompt_speech` em "
"vez de `reference_audio` e `prompt_text` em vez de `reference_text` para "
"fornecer o áudio de referência para o modelo FishSpeech. Esse parâmetro é "
"consistente com a clonagem de voz do CosyVoice."

