#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:578
msgid ""
"Now SenseVoiceSmall use a small vad model ``fsmn-vad``, it will be "
"downloaded thus network required."
msgstr ""
"Agora o SenseVoiceSmall usa um pequeno modelo VAD `fsmn-vad`, portanto ele "
"precisa de uma rede para download."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:580
msgid "For offline environment, you can download the vad model in advance."
msgstr ""
"Em ambientes offline, você pode baixar este modelo VAD com antecedência."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:582
msgid ""
"Download from `huggingface <https://huggingface.co/funasr/fsmn-vad>`_ or "
"`modelscope <https://modelscope.cn/models/iic/speech_fsmn_vad_zh-"
"cn-16k-common-pytorch/files>`_. Assume downloaded to ``/path/to/fsmn-vad``."
msgstr ""
"Baixe do `huggingface <https://huggingface.co/funasr/fsmn-vad>`_ ou "
"`modelscope <https://modelscope.cn/models/iic/speech_fsmn_vad_zh-"
"cn-16k-common-pytorch/files>`_. Suponha que o download seja feito para "
"``/path/to/fsmn-vad``."

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/audio.rst:585
msgid ""
"Then when launching SenseVoiceSmall with Web UI, you can add an additional "
"parameter with key ``vad_model`` and value ``/path/to/fsmn-vad`` which is "
"the downloaded path. When launching with command line, you can add an option"
" ``--vad_model /path/to/fsmn-vad``."
msgstr ""
"Em seguida, ao carregar o SenseVoiceSmall com a Web UI, adicione uma opção "
"extra: a chave é ``vad_model``, e o valor é o caminho de download anterior "
"``/path/to/fsmn-vad``. Ao carregar via linha de comando, adicione a opção "
"``--vad_model /path/to/fsmn-vad``."

